# infrastructure-engineering-assignment
Scan the drivers and identify top 10 largest file on system
Program takes two arguments, first source folder and destination folder
- To run the program type the following in cmd prompt or terminal
    python infra.py <source folder> <destination folder>
  It scan the source folder and store all the contents having different file extension
  according to their extension in the foldsr having name that of extension and information
  about its size. Out of which top 10 largest file are displayed. 
